{
  "id": "69a9c445fd37cc199173dc39",
  "title": "英語にダイアクリティカルマーク付き文字を導入する",
  "created": 1772733652,
  "updated": 1772873148,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a9c445fd37cc199173dc39",
      "text": "英語にダイアクリティカルマーク付き文字を導入する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772733652,
      "updated": 1772734503
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9c80e0000000000b6171d",
      "text": "[英語]に[ダイアクリティカルマーク付き文字を導入する]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772734479,
      "updated": 1772734487
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9c8280000000000b6171e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772734504,
      "updated": 1772734504
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab0dd00000000004ca753",
      "text": "英語母語話者がしばしば[ダイアクリティカルマーク]付き文字を別の文字として認識しておらず、無視したり消したりする傾向があることに着目した[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772794078,
      "updated": 1772795945
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab11400000000007ee527",
      "text": "基礎の部分のリサーチが足りない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772794133,
      "updated": 1772794135
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaadee00000000004ca579",
      "text": "\t20世紀に行われた[英語教育のために綴字体系を改変する試み]の多くは、（字上符付き文字とは別の）字母を追加するものだったようだ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772793328,
      "updated": 1772805229
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab15000000000007ee529",
      "text": "\t\t[Initial Teaching Alphabet] (ITA)",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772794193,
      "updated": 1772794217
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab18b00000000007ee52b",
      "text": "\t\t[Unifon alphabet]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772794252,
      "updated": 1772794271
    },
    {
      "id": "69aadefa0000000000932135",
      "text": "\t\t[Shavian alphabet] (ラテン文字ではなく独自の文字体系)",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772805883,
      "updated": 1772805948
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab40000000000007ee52d",
      "text": "\t\tこれらは元の綴りから字面を大きく変更するため、正式な綴りを追加で覚えるコストが発生した",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772794881,
      "updated": 1772805875
    },
    {
      "id": "69aadeef0000000000932134",
      "text": " ああ、文中の登場位置次第で単語のアクセントが変化するパターンを把握しなければ…",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772805872,
      "updated": 1772805994
    },
    {
      "id": "69aae109000000000093213c",
      "text": " \t単語レベルなら別にいいか",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772806410,
      "updated": 1772806425
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaae7500000000005fc18c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793462,
      "updated": 1772793462
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaae3d00000000005fc18a",
      "text": "細かい発音よりも強勢位置をダイアクリティカルマークで示される方が分かりやすい[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793406,
      "updated": 1772793491
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab28600000000004ca755",
      "text": "\t\t確かに[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772794504,
      "updated": 1772794516
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaae7600000000005fc18d",
      "text": "\tというのも英語の母音の細かい違いは強勢に由来することが多く、強勢に点をつけるだけで結果的に発音の細かい違いを区別することができる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793463,
      "updated": 1772793536
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaec000000000005fc18e",
      "text": "\t\t特に曖昧母音 ə は強勢の無いところで発生する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793537,
      "updated": 1772794080
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaedf00000000005fc18f",
      "text": "\t\ttable:母音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793567,
      "updated": 1772793622
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaf2800000000005fc194",
      "text": "\t\t \t前\t中\t奥",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793641,
      "updated": 1772793945
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaf1600000000005fc190",
      "text": "\t\t 狭\ti/ɪ\t\tʊ/ʌ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793622,
      "updated": 1772793934
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaf1b00000000005fc191",
      "text": "\t\t 中\te/ɛ/ɜ\tə\to/ɔ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793628,
      "updated": 1772793941
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaaf2100000000005fc192",
      "text": "\t\t 広\ta\ta\ta",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793634,
      "updated": 1772793956
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaae4a00000000005fc18b",
      "text": "  ↑これを、↓こうする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793418,
      "updated": 1772794001
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd102000000000078d3a2",
      "text": "  \tもうこれで完成で良いのでは…[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772867843,
      "updated": 1772872929
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe4dd000000000078d486",
      "text": "  \t\tこれが書かれたときによく見ていなかった😇",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872926,
      "updated": 1772872945
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab01700000000005fc19c",
      "text": "\t\ttable:母音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793879,
      "updated": 1772793988
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab01700000000005fc19d",
      "text": "\t\t \t前\t奥",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793879,
      "updated": 1772793988
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab01700000000005fc19e",
      "text": "\t\t 狭\tí/i\tú/u",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793879,
      "updated": 1772793988
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab01700000000005fc19f",
      "text": "\t\t 中\té/e\tó/o",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793879,
      "updated": 1772793988
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab01700000000005fc1a0",
      "text": "\t\t 広\tá/a\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793879,
      "updated": 1772793988
    },
    {
      "id": "69abc66700000000008d5e05",
      "text": " \t[Nrem.icon] 表は表の直後にインデントするとセル内に入ってしまうから、どこに返信を書くべきか悩ましい",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772865129,
      "updated": 1772865255
    },
    {
      "id": "69abc68e00000000008d5e0e",
      "text": " \t\t\tああ、アイコン前置きすればいいのか",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772865167,
      "updated": 1772865225
    },
    {
      "id": "69abc66d00000000008d5e09",
      "text": " \t\t強勢のない部分はやはり書き分けの余地があるのかもしれない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772865135,
      "updated": 1772865205
    },
    {
      "id": "69abc66700000000008d5e08",
      "text": " \t 一旦スペリングのパターンに最適化されていない粗雑で複雑な案を完成させる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772865129,
      "updated": 1772865233
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab01000000000005fc196",
      "text": "  二重母音は二重母音らしく2文字の合字にして上に点を乗せるといい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772793873,
      "updated": 1772794049
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab0c100000000005fc1a1",
      "text": "  \tよく強勢が来るから",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772794050,
      "updated": 1772794084
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab10f00000000005fc1a2",
      "text": "  \te'i, e'a, o'u, ... ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772794127,
      "updated": 1772794169
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab24e00000000004ca754",
      "text": "  \t合字は元の綴りの字面が変わってしまうので私の案としては避けたい[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772794447,
      "updated": 1772794554
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab15300000000005fc1a3",
      "text": "  あんまり細かく分けても使い勝手が悪い。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772794196,
      "updated": 1772794237
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab17d00000000005fc1a4",
      "text": "  \t理屈的には最も多くの言語の発音を表せるはずの IPA がどの言語でも常用されていないことからも想像できることだろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772794237,
      "updated": 1772794277
    },
    {
      "id": "69aab01000000000005fc195",
      "text": "\t\t\tごもっともです[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772793873,
      "updated": 1772867864
    },
    {
      "id": "69aadeb30000000000932132",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772805812,
      "updated": 1772805812
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd134000000000078d3a3",
      "text": "飽きた😇[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772867893,
      "updated": 1772867953
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd137000000000078d3a4",
      "text": "\tCosenseの表の操作が面倒。紙とペンのほうが圧倒的に速い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772867896,
      "updated": 1772872968
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd157000000000078d3a5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772867928,
      "updated": 1772867928
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a6000000000078d487",
      "text": "以下、残骸",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873127,
      "updated": 1772873142
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d488",
      "text": "table: ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d489",
      "text": "table:符号なし",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d48a",
      "text": "\ta\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d48b",
      "text": "\to\t/ɒ/\t/ɑ/\tlOt",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d48c",
      "text": "\tu\t/ʊ/\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d48d",
      "text": "\te\t/ɛ/\t\tbed, set, head",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d48e",
      "text": "\ti\t/ɪ/\t\tsit, milk",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d48f",
      "text": "table:開母音化 `'`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d490",
      "text": "\tá\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d491",
      "text": "\tó\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d492",
      "text": "\tú\t/ʌ/\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d493",
      "text": "\té\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d494",
      "text": "\tí\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d495",
      "text": "table:閉母音化 ```",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d496",
      "text": "\tà\t/ɒ/\t/ɔː/\t\twatch, what",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d497",
      "text": "\tò\t/ʊ/\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d498",
      "text": "\tù\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d499",
      "text": "\tè\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d49a",
      "text": "\tì\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d49b",
      "text": "table:口唇分離化 `¨`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d49c",
      "text": "\tä\t/æ/\t\tcät, mäp, händ, bäth, päth, gläss",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d49d",
      "text": "\tö\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d49e",
      "text": "\tü\t/juː/\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d49f",
      "text": "\tür\t/ɜː/\t/ɜr/, /b/\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d4a0",
      "text": "\të\t/ɜː/\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d4a1",
      "text": "\tï\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d4a2",
      "text": "table:長母音化 `¯`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d4a3",
      "text": "\tĀ\t/ɑː/\t\t\tfāther, pālm, spā",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d4a4",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tbáth, pāth, glāss",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d4a5",
      "text": "\tŌ\t/uː/\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d4a6",
      "text": "\tÔU\t/ɔː/\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d4a7",
      "text": "\tŪ\t/uː/\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d4a8",
      "text": "\tÊ\t/iː/\t\t\tbē, mē, thēme",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d4a9",
      "text": "\tÎ\t/iː/\t\t\tmachīne, polīce",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d4aa",
      "text": "table:二重母音化 `^`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe5a7000000000078d4ab",
      "text": "\tÂ\t/eɪ/\t\t*\tcâke, nâme, tâble",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873128,
      "updated": 1772873128
    },
